<TEXT>
<P>
GAZA, July 26 (Xinhua) -- Secretary General of the Palestinian
National Authority (PNA) Ahmed Abdurahman on Monday welcomed the
meeting to be held in Cairo in early August between PNA Chairman
Yasser Arafat and leaders of the Palestinian opposition factions.
</P>
