Meanwhile, he urged Iraq to comply with the United Nations
Security Council resolutions.
</P>
<P>
The U.N. Security Council imposed sweeping economic sanctions
on Iraq in 1990 after its invasion of Kuwait. Iraq blames the
sanctions for the shortage of food and medicine suffered by its
people. 
