communications center to operate over the crucial date change
period to ensure they were kept informed of developments and able
to communicate with the government and other parties about any
necessary action.
</P>
<P>
Costello said financial sector regulators actively encouraged
disclosure by financial institutions as a means of maintaining
confidence of customers and other market players.
</P>
<P>
