<TEXT>
<P>
CHONGQING, July 27 (Xinhua) -- Fifteen people were killed and
47 injured in an explosion this morning in Changshou County,
Chongqing Municipality in southwest China.
</P>
<P>
At 9:15 a.m. today, a truck carrying detonators for a local
fuel plant suddenly exploded as it passed the residential area of
Fengcheng Township in the county.
</P>
<P>
The severe explosion destroyed a four-storey hotel. Fortunately,
most of the guests were out at the time of the explosion.
</P>
