<HEADLINE> Pakistan Denies Letting Others Use Its Soil </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, July 27 (Xinhua) -- Pakistani Minister of State for
Foreign Affairs Siddique Kanju categorically stated Tuesday that
Pakistan will not allow any country to use its territory for
launching attacks against other countries.
</P>
<P>
