<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Stocks Rebound </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, July 27 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks increased 208.
57 points, or 1.62 percent, to close at 13,075.09 Tuesday.
</P>
