<HEADLINE> Germany Wins Women's 4x200m Freestyle Relay </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, July 27 (Xinhua) -- Germany won the women's 4x200
meters freestyle relay at the European Swimming Championship in
Istanbul Tuesday morning.
</P>
<P>
In the championship at the Atakoy Olympic Natatorium, the
German team won the gold medal with 8:14.92. Britain finished
second with 8:15.05 and Belgium third at 8:19.04. 
</P>
