</P>
<P>
SINGAPORE -- China said on Tuesday that upholding the principle
of sovereignty has become all the more necessary in the present-
day world where there is a severe lack of equilibrium in the
balance of power.
</P>
<P>
In a speech to a dialogue meeting in Singapore between ASEAN
and its dialogue partners, Chinese Foreign Minister Tang Jiaxuan
also stressed the importance of respect for the role and authority
of the United Nations. (Singapore-China-Tang)
</P>
